/**
 * [onLoad()]
 * Runs on loading of the script.
 * 
 * In this script:
 *  Creates all graphics shown in the menu.
 *  Changes the discord status. 
 *  If the player hasn't seen this, marks this sequence as completed in the save data.
*/
